sqlParams.paramVal:
SELECT 'MAX_KEY' AS max_key, COALESCE(MAX(offering_key) ,0)
FROM dim_offering;

properties.propertyVal:
SELECT DISTINCT
	SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_KEY AS TEST_TYPE_KEY
	,SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_ID AS TEST_TYPE_ID
	,SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_NAME AS TEST_TYPE_NAME
	,SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_DESCRIPTION AS TEST_TYPE_DESCRIPTION
	,SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_TABLE_NAME AS TEST_TYPE_TABLE_NAME
	,SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_CODE_NAME AS TEST_TYPE_CODE_NAME
	,SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_LAB_ID AS TEST_TYPE_LAB_ID
	,SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_CREATED_ON AS TEST_TYPE_CREATED_ON
	,SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_UPDATED_ON AS TEST_TYPE_UPDATED_ON
	,SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_ACTIVE AS TEST_TYPE_ACTIVE
	,SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_LOW_CUTOFF AS TEST_TYPE_LOW_CUTOFF
	,SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_HIGH_CUTOFF AS TEST_TYPE_HIGH_CUTOFF
	,SRC_dim_test_type.POSITION AS POSITION
	,SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_ICON AS TEST_TYPE_ICON
	,SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_FUNCTION AS TEST_TYPE_FUNCTION
	,SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_SHORT AS TEST_TYPE_SHORT
	,SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_VIDEO_URL AS TEST_TYPE_VIDEO_URL
	,SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_PROVIDER_CODES AS TEST_TYPE_PROVIDER_CODES
	,SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_LAB_SUPPLIES AS TEST_TYPE_LAB_SUPPLIES
	,SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_LABCORP_CODE AS TEST_TYPE_LABCORP_CODE
	,SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_VACCINATION AS TEST_TYPE_VACCINATION
	,SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_VENIPUNCTURE AS TEST_TYPE_VENIPUNCTURE
	,SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_BODY_MEASUREMENTS AS TEST_TYPE_BODY_MEASUREMENTS
	,SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_DELETED_AT AS TEST_TYPE_DELETED_AT
	,SRC_dim_test_type.VERSION AS VERSION
	,SRC_dim_test_type.EFFECTIVE_AT AS EFFECTIVE_AT
	,SRC_dim_test_type.TERM_AT AS TERM_AT
	,SRC_dim_test_type.IS_CURRENT AS IS_CURRENT
	,SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_SAMPLING AS TEST_TYPE_SAMPLING
	,COALESCE(SRC_dim_screening_offering.SCREENING_METHOD_KIND,'Not Provided') AS SCREENING_METHOD_KIND
	 FROM 
	$DO_GHL1_MY_MYSQL_DIM_TEST_TYPE SRC_dim_test_type 
join fact_test SRC_fact_test on SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_KEY=SRC_fact_test.TEST_TYPE_KEY  
join dim_screening_offering SRC_dim_screening_offering on SRC_fact_test.SCREENING_OFFERING_KEY = SRC_dim_screening_offering.SCREENING_OFFERING_KEY 
WHERE 
-- ifnull(SRC_fact_test.is_deleted ,0)!=1 and  -- (changed on 09JUL2019 to capture all records in associated fact tables)
SRC_dim_test_type.IS_CURRENT=1

attributes.attrExprVal: case when SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_DELETED_AT is null then 0 else 1 end

dCmd_Inst.dCmd:
UPDATE control_load_history
SET status = 'FAILED', 
finish_timestamp = $$CurrentTimeStamp,
updated_at = $$CurrentTimeStamp
WHERE data_flow_name = 'DF_LOAD_dim_offering_V3_ODS' AND status= 'RUNNING';

UPDATE control_load_history
SET status = 'ABORTED', 
finish_timestamp = $$CurrentTimeStamp,
updated_at = $$CurrentTimeStamp
WHERE data_flow_name ='DF_LOAD_dim_offering_V3_ODS' AND status= 'RUNNING';

INSERT INTO control_load_history (data_flow_name, status, start_timestamp, created_at)
VALUES ('DF_LOAD_dim_offering_V3_ODS', 'RUNNING', $$CurrentTimeStamp, $$CurrentTimeStamp);

UPDATE control_load_history
SET status = 'SUCCEEDED', 
finish_timestamp = $$CurrentTimeStamp,
SRC_source_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_dim_offering_V3_ODS.SRC_dim_test_type.SourceCount  , 
SRC_process_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_dim_offering_V3_ODS.SRC_dim_test_type.ProcessCount  , 
SRC_target_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_dim_offering_V3_ODS.SRC_dim_test_type.TargetCount  , 
SRC_bad_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_dim_offering_V3_ODS.SRC_dim_test_type.BadCount  ,
TGT_source_count =   $RST_DF_LOAD_dim_offering_V3_ODS.TGT_dim_offering.SourceCount  , 
TGT_process_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_dim_offering_V3_ODS.TGT_dim_offering.ProcessCount  , 
TGT_target_count  =  $RST_DF_LOAD_dim_offering_V3_ODS.TGT_dim_offering.TargetCount   , 
TGT_bad_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_dim_offering_V3_ODS.TGT_dim_offering.BadCount   ,
updated_at = $$CurrentTimeStamp
WHERE data_flow_name = 'DF_LOAD_dim_offering_V3_ODS' AND status= 'RUNNING'
